        <h2 style="color: var(--paper);">Whether you&rsquo;re a Florida buyer working with an attorney on trust ownership, FIRPTA compliance, or estate planning &mdash; or an attorney looking for a mortgage yourself &mdash; Stairway coordinates the mortgage side with the depth your attorney partner expects.</h2>
